lead_paragraph: The doctor, Robert Rho, pleaded not guilty after he was charged in Queens with second-degree manslaughter in the death of a patient from abortion complications.

headline.print_headline: Doctor Is Charged in Death After an Abortion
headline.main: Queens Doctor Is Charged in Woman’s Death After Abortion Procedure

snippet: The doctor, Robert Rho, pleaded not guilty after he was charged in Queens with second-degree manslaughter in the death of a patient from abortion complications....
abstract: Dr Robert Rho is charged with manslaughter after patient Jaime Lee Morales dies as result of complications from abortion he performed in Queens clinic.
